text.tspan: Director at the nonprofit Local Connectivity Lab (LCL). Founded the Seattle Community Network
(SCN), where we build DIY Internet infrastructure for digital equity.
Associate professor in the department of Human Centered Design & Engineering (HCDE) at the
University of Washington where she directs the Machine Agency
Director of Open Technology at Open Earth Foundation, Co-creator of ActivityPub, Founder of
social web projects such as: Wikitravel, StatusNet, identi.ca, Fuzzy.ai, GNU Social.
Chair of the board at Software Freedom Conservancy, board member at LLVM Foundation,
governing board member at CHERI Alliance and OpenInfra Foundation
Community and Culture, Open Hardware, Languages & Tools, Cloud and Infrastructure,
